			<h1><span class="less"><a href="index.html">SLE 2021</a> paper:</span><br><i>There is More Than One Way to Zen Your Python</i></h1>
			<h2><a href="../profile/AamirFarooq.html">Aamir Farooq</a>, <a href="../profile/VadimZaytsev.html">Vadim Zaytsev</a></h2>
